WEBVTT

00:01:28.504 --> 00:01:31.204
and I felt that this
amazing way of making forests

00:01:31.234 --> 00:01:34.754
should not stay limited
just to our factory.

00:01:34.784 --> 00:01:39.174
So I made a forest in my home,
which looks something like this now.

00:01:39.204 --> 00:01:42.904
(Applause)

00:01:45.344 --> 00:01:47.800
After building a forest at home,

00:01:47.824 --> 00:01:51.720
I stopped making cars
and started making forests.

00:01:51.744 --> 00:01:54.600
Since then, we have planted 
more than a hundred forests

00:01:54.624 --> 00:01:58.560
in 35 cities across the world.

00:01:58.584 --> 00:02:01.960
